WEBVTT

00:03:58.289 --> 00:04:02.780
even allow myself
to reinvent myself at times.

00:04:03.393 --> 00:04:06.666
So for example, in high school,

00:04:06.690 --> 00:04:08.700
I have to confess I was a mega-nerd.

00:04:08.724 --> 00:04:12.327
I had no sense of fashion --
thick glasses, simple hairstyle --

00:04:12.351 --> 00:04:13.696
you can get the idea.

00:04:13.720 --> 00:04:18.013
I think, actually, I only had friends
because I shared my homework.

00:04:18.037 --> 00:04:19.187
That's the truth.

00:04:19.627 --> 00:04:21.659
But once at university,

00:04:21.683 --> 00:04:25.377
I was able to find
a new identity for myself,

00:04:25.401 --> 00:04:29.371
and the nerd became a popular girl.